@InteractHub_API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5153
@AccessToken = paste-jwt-token-here

GET {{InteractHub_API_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

# API moi them ngay 2026-05-02

### Profile - lay profile hien tai
GET {{InteractHub_API_HostAddress}}/api/Profile/me
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Profile - lay profile theo userId
GET {{InteractHub_API_HostAddress}}/api/Profile/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Profile - cap nhat profile hien tai
PUT {{InteractHub_API_HostAddress}}/api/Profile/me
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenTaiKhoan": "Nguyen Van A",
  "email": "nguyenvana@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "0900000000",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar.png",
  "bio": "Hello InteractHub",
  "ngaySinh": "2004-01-01T00:00:00",
  "gioiTinh": "Nam",
  "diaChi": "Ho Chi Minh City"
}

###

### Profile - doi mat khau
POST {{InteractHub_API_HostAddress}}/api/Profile/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "OldPassword123!",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123!",
  "confirmPassword": "NewPassword123!"
}

###

### Profile - upload avatar
POST {{InteractHub_API_HostAddress}}/api/Profile/upload-avatar
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=avatarBoundary

--avatarBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="avatar.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./avatar.png
--avatarBoundary--

###

### Profile - follow/unfollow user
POST {{InteractHub_API_HostAddress}}/api/Profile/{{userId}}/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Profile - followers
GET {{InteractHub_API_HostAddress}}/api/Profile/{{userId}}/followers?page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Profile - following
GET {{InteractHub_API_HostAddress}}/api/Profile/{{userId}}/following?page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Friendship - gui yeu cau ket ban
POST {{InteractHub_API_HostAddress}}/api/Friendship/{{recipientId}}/request
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Friendship - chap nhan yeu cau ket ban
POST {{InteractHub_API_HostAddress}}/api/Friendship/{{senderId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Post - feed
GET {{InteractHub_API_HostAddress}}/api/Post/feed?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###
